{"word":"κατέρχομαι","slug":"κατέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰατέρχομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔρχομαι\">ἔρχομαι</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> come/go down,</b> of moving in a geographical context without necessarily implying descent or ascent, which may or may not be signaled by context <b><a href='B:490 4:31'>Lk 4:31</a>; <a href='B:490 9:37'>9:37</a>; <a href='B:510 8:5'>Ac 8:5</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Ac.; <b><a href='B:660 3:15'>Js 3:15</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as nautical <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ t.t.\">t.t.</a> <b>arrive, put in <a href='B:510 21:3'>Ac 21:3</a>; <a href='B:510 27:5'>27:5</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κατεργάζομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κατεσθίω/κατέσθω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}